concept_class.name: Test
concept_class.description: Acq. during patient encounter (vitals, labs, etc.)

concept_class.name: Misc
concept_class.description: Terms which don't fit other categories

concept_class.name: Symptom/Finding
concept_class.description: Observation that can be reported from patient or found on exam

concept_class.name: Misc Order
concept_class.description: Orderable items which aren't tests or drugs

concept_class.name: Workflow
concept_class.description: A workflow within a treatment program

concept_datatype.name: Numeric
concept_datatype.description: Numeric value, including integer or float (e.g., creatinine, weight)

concept_datatype.name: Coded
concept_datatype.description: Value determined by term dictionary lookup (i.e., term identifier)

concept_datatype.name: N/A
concept_datatype.description: Not associated with a datatype (e.g., term answers, sets)

concept_datatype.name: Document
concept_datatype.description: Pointer to a binary or text-based document (e.g., clinical document, RTF, XML, EKG, image, etc.) stored in complex_obs table

concept_datatype.name: Complex
concept_datatype.description: Complex value. Analogous to HL7 Embedded Datatype
